{"tid":2358634,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"iTunes出左亞基拉4K remaster版","createTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T16:37:03.000Z","uid":134683,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4309e18bc77b55d53b44014a79ca3716464ac221","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"日本動畫嘅蒙羅麗莎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXa7kxQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXa7kxQ.png&h=ed35cb1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62ccd05cf5402ce5aa1eef926e63f093745e25b5","tid":2358634,"uid":220431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"2020東京奧運已經無法如期舉行"},{"pid":"d98a2e554d3fac00fa441d82d1d4ddf8394298d1","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnXp7uc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnXp7uc.jpg&h=e291815d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2584344704e4afd8167bd8c4011c99de96c2c7ce","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"好彩早幾個月前可以喺戲院睇到呢套4K版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee9040582df24d8981eeb0501e00053daeee791","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"阿基拉既成功唔單只係個故事改得好<br />\n更加重要係技術層面上到今時今日都好難做到<br />\n開拍之前好多人都唔睇好<br />\n因為漫畫作畫太精細<br />\n當年亦因為太大製作要幾間大公司合資先拍得成<br />\n動畫膠片數破左天空之城紀錄<br />\n日本動畫一向都只係一秒12格左右甚至更少<br />\n有別於迪士尼1秒24格既標準<br />\n而角色講説話都只係個口一開一合<br />\n呢啲方法係手塚治蟲為左節省成本令動畫可以響電視上播而發明<br />\n但阿基拉好多時用足1秒24格<br />\n角色講話係全個身都郁<br />\n膠片數目大增<br />\n所以動作特別連貫<br />\n而且電單車上面既燈光同殘像要用曡影呢啲拍攝技術<br />\n難度高過一般動畫好多<br />\n配音亦同一般動畫唔同係先配音後作畫<br />\n要動畫師遷就返配音<br />\n配樂係藝能山城組<br />\n亦都係先由佢哋作曲<br />\n大友克洋對佢哋完全信任<br />\n採用印尼甘美朗敲擊音樂作為主要風格<br />\n樂器都要專程去搵返黎<br />\n錄音方面<br />\n佢地用無定向咪去營造特別音效<br />\n亦都係首先用電腦做mixing<br />\n所以呢套阿基拉絕對係日本動畫史上既蒙羅麗莎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f12e89f6292d17b8b8d33ed9d1ec41797c80480","tid":2358634,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"勁係勁但點解係蒙羅麗莎"},{"pid":"620a81a659809afa4f51cb5b8e3465cad10ee6c9","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f12e89f6292d17b8b8d33ed9d1ec41797c80480","tid":2358634,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"勁係勁但點解係蒙羅麗莎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"精緻程度同藝術品有得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb6e00501ab14b78cc7625beb6a1929c606b0a5","tid":2358634,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2584344704e4afd8167bd8c4011c99de96c2c7ce","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"好彩早幾個月前可以喺戲院睇到呢套4K版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"Element睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce65f88c9a1fcf3454135e824fa78dc46a5bafa","tid":2358634,"uid":152367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"買日版4K碟收藏啦"},{"pid":"843cb41f5eb3637e3778dc2835672e527d488d34","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cce65f88c9a1fcf3454135e824fa78dc46a5bafa","tid":2358634,"uid":152367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"買日版4K碟收藏啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"暫時只睇到apple tv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb67a418283a8b04f4cbc29c8b63ce5ea32be1b","tid":2358634,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"係戲院睇<br />\n啲配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff17e40120c527e730b9bef38b0562de8e7ce30","tid":2358634,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6eb67a418283a8b04f4cbc29c8b63ce5ea32be1b","tid":2358634,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"係戲院睇<br />\n啲配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"本身隻soundtrack已經係試機天碟<br />\n每次換player同耳機都一定用呢隻soundtrack黎試機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢次重新上映4K版<br />\n可能係呢套戲嘅最後一次<br />\n好難得可以喺戲院級音響重新演繹<br />\n一開場嗰幾吓鼓聲<br />\n已經好明顯話俾觀眾知音響方面比上次Blu-ray化更進一步<br />\n成套戲簡直係聲畫兩方面最高享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當日好多人都留低聽完ending先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}